    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#p305# asked for my help one last time, this time to hunt #r200 #o38#s#k and collect #b200 #t4000033#s#k. I wonder why she needs so many... Is she trying to sell them or something?"
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I eliminated a bunch of #o38#s in a forest near #m10002000# and collected all #b200 #t4000033#s#k for #p305#. In return, she gave me a nice hat. I've collected so many dolls for her, but it seems like the #o38#s aren't decreasing in any way, shape, or form... I wonder what's going on. However, it seems that the fairies may not have as much animosity toward humans now... at least that's a good thing."
    },
